name: Typhoon Haiyan Relief T-Shirt
description:
Raise Money for The Philippines Typhoon Relief Fund

On November 8, 2013, the lives of millions of Filipino residents were forever altered by Typhoon Haiyan, one of the strongest storms ever recorded. To give much-needed assistance to those who have lost their homes and livelihood, FLIPCORE will be contributing 80% of the proceeds from this shirt to support the emergency appeal.

We will also be donating directly to the victims, buying them supplies and essentials.

This is a Limited Edition garment and it will be our Final Release of 2013. It is hand printed in London, UK with premium quality paint and materials. Our post-delivery date will be on the 24th Nov.

Buying 1 shirt can feed a family for 2 weeks with rice, food & water. 80% of your money will be donated to help the victims of Typhoon Haiyan who currently have no home or anything left. We are appreciative for every customer supporting this cause.

There is a part in Northern Cebu that really needs attention, and the Red Cross is not helping that area nor is it aware or being shown on the News!!! We have photos and videos we will be showing, as well as showing what impact and difference you make in people's live by just buying 1 shirt.

YOU can make a CHANGE. Help the less fortunate, and save a life today.

This statement is very moving and powerful, as its a tribute to those Typhoon Haiyan victims. Wear with honor & pride.
